Package io.servicetalk.grpc.api

Interface GrpcSerializationProvider

@Deprecated public interface GrpcSerializationProvider
Deprecated.
Serialization is now specified via MethodDescriptor. Compression is configured per route. gRPC framing is internalized in the gRPC implementation.
A provider for gRPC serialization/deserialization.
